criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients with ultrasonographic diagnosis of uterine myomas

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  patients with previous incomplete hysteroscopic myoma resection;

          -  patients undergoing additional surgical procedures performed by hysteroscopy (such as,
             resection of endometrial polyps);

          -  patients undergoing associated non-hysteroscopic surgical procedures;

          -  patients with severe cardiovascular disease, decompensated diabetes and severe
             hematologic disorders
